definitions.definition: The process of moving an idea from concept to reality . In business , engineering and other fields, implementation refers to the building process rather than the design process.
examples: Now that the requirements are complete we can move on to implementation .

definitions.definition: A result of implementing something; a finished product , system or device .
examples: His implementation works, but it needs some fine-tuning.
